<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Max-depth override rejection - parent depth preserved</title>
</head>
<body>
invalid (alpha) keeps parent depth: [included: [Hello World]]
invalid (negative) keeps parent depth: [included: [Hello World]]
invalid (decimal) keeps parent depth: [included: [Hello World]]
invalid (above documented maximum) keeps parent depth: [included: [Hello World]]
invalid (huge uint64 value) keeps parent depth: [included: [Hello World]]
invalid (beyond uint64) keeps parent depth: [included: [Hello World]]
valid override above parent depth honours parent: [included: [Hello World]]
valid override at parent depth matches parent: [included: [Hello World]]
empty max-depth is treated as no override: [included: [Hello World]]
whitespace-only max-depth is treated as no override: [included: [Hello World]]
</body>
</html>
